texts.text: >On distant Mount Kailash...
>A meditating Shiva slowly opens his eyes.

This feeling...
The evil thoughts of Man...
O how it has grown in its intensity...
Evil's return is imminent, but his counterpart has yet to awaken...
Then I shall descend to the to the human world and give aid.

Angra Mainyu...
He must not rise again.
>At a certain high school in Japan,
>A crowd of students is gathered around a single male student.
Hi Haru, how about we have lunch together?
Hey, not fair! You should eat lunch with me, Mr. student council president!
Let's all have lunch together! Problem solved! Right Haru?
We want to eat with Haru, not you!

*Chuckle*
Alright everyone, just calm down. I already have an appointment today, so...
Haru!
>Someone is calling to the student named Haru from outside the ring of people surrounding him.

Fuyuki!
What took you so long?
Ahaha, things happened and I was delayed... But everything's been taken care of!
Haru, you're having lunch with Fuyuki again?
Yes. After all, I made a promise.
Seriously, what is it with you and him though? Don't you think you're a bit too close?
Well, we've been friends for ages. What wrong with us hanging out?
Yeah, the friends for ages thing... But you two are actually more like...
What is it Haru. Are you going to have lunch with these people today?
No, I'll be with you in a minute. After all, I made a promise.
Sorry guys, maybe next time!
>After school.
>A certain student is surrounded by a bunch of other students.
Hey, what's your relationship with Haru anyway?
Even if you had an appointment, you kept him waiting! Who the hell are you to keep the student council president waiting?
What? I can't hear you. Speak up.
I don't know why Haru would hang out with you. You're so lame.
Or did you think hanging out with Haru would make you cool?
That's what you're after right?
N-No!
I just thought it'd be nice if I could help Haru out a bit......
So umm... This wasn't about me...
I told you to speak up!
S-Sorry...
Don't you know you're not good enough to be around Haru?
It's not about being good enough, we're just friends...
Even though I'm like this, I can still...
Fuyuki! There you are!
Oops...
Oh shit...
Hi guys. What are you doing here with Fuyuki?
H-Haru...
I just wanted to do something for you, so...
(So it has awakened. The Evil within.)
You... You're...
(Yes, fill yourself with hatred for him. Show them just how great your hate is.)
(Unleash the darkness you have nurtured for so long. Hit them with all you have pent up inside.)
Fuyuki...?
What the hell's wrong with him? What a freak.
Y-Your light shines so bright, that's why I... I...!
(Bond with me, and take your revenge...! Be one with Angra Mainyu!)
*Scream*
(Hehehe... Hahahahahah! That's it! Give in to me!)
(The seed of Evil planted by my minion the serpent has finally bore fruit!)
Fuyuki! What's the matter?!
Fuyu-
Fuck off!
This doesn't look good. Let's get outta here.
Where do you think you're going?
Wha-
>Before the girl can utter a word, Fuyuki makes his move.
Ugh...
Oof...
>Everyone there except Haru is rendered unconscious...
Fuyuki, what are you doing...
Stay away from me, hero wannabe.
Wha-?!

I didn't mean to...
Don't you recognize me?!
>Ignoring the pleadings of Haru,
>Fuyuki grabs the unconscious students and disappears...
>Immediately afterwards, the entire school is enveloped by a strange atmosphere.
Why? What happened Fuyuki...?
>But Haru does not notice.
Greetings, Son of Man.
Son of Man, Haru!
W-What?! There's a voice...
I am Shiva, god of destruction and rebirth.
The human you call Fuyuki has been possessed by an Evil deity.
If this Evil is not defeated, the human Fuyuki will be lost.
No! G-Gods and Evil...?! What are you talking about?
I too, wish to defeat this Evil. The god called Angra Mainyu.
If we do not stop him, the world will be filled with malice,
and the world will quickly come to an end.
What am I supposed to do? I'm just a normal human being...
I will aid you.
Huh...?
All you need to do is let me use your body to manifest in this plain of existence.
If you do...
If I do that, will Fuyuki be saved?! Will I be able to save him?!
Yes.
...Alright then. I'll lend you my body.
Good. Then we have a pact.
>A white smoke rises up around Haru and takes on the form of a demon...
We shall defeat Angra Mainyu, the epitome of Evil.
Everyone's here, I hope?
That's right Gatekeeper! It's not like you to be this serious though, so what's wrong?
That's a rude thing to say. I'm always serious.
Just kiddin' aight? My bad.
So what's the matter at hand? You said you felt somethin' strange.
Guys, don't you feel that people in general have been kind of on edge lately?
Not just lately. It's been like that a long time now.
It's kind of a sad thing to be agreeing with, but yes you're right.
To us though, that is very troubling.
Am I right, Taro?
Yeah.
And I get what you're trying to say, Gatekeeper.
In recent weeks,
there have been a lot small conflicts happenin' all over town.
Oh I noticed that too!
These days, I see customers arguing with each other a lot when I'm working at the cafe.
Things like that used to happen from time to time before, but it's way worse now.
I'm sure we all noticed little things like that, and I think the cause of it is...
The Dragon!
This school becoming an Aura Gate? Wasn't expecting that...
You know this school?
Yeah it's kinda famous for giving the students a lot of freedom. It's their sales pitch.
Like even though there's a uniform, you don't really have to wear it. You can just wear your own clothes to school if you want.
That is pretty unique.
But deciding what to wear is a pain in the ass anyway, so I'd prefer the uniform.
I'd go with uniform too. Less laundry!
I'm not sure that's how a high school girl should think...
Got a problem?

So... Dragon huh?
You know what that's about, Mr. Meat?
>With Seiran guiding their way, the Liberators find themselves in a high school turned Aura Gate.
>The team is now searching for survivors.
Heck if I know. Maybe we kill one?
If only it were that easy.
Even though it's called the Dragon Stream, hearing a dragon's voice is anything but normal.
But lately, a dragon's voice can be heard sporadically coming from the Dragon Stream.
And it's getting louder.
Then there's this new Aura Gate that mysteriously appeared around the same time...
Yeah, they're definitely connected.
My thoughts exactly. So, let's keep searching.
Got it. The thing is, we haven't found a single...
Hey look! Over there, Mr. Meat!
>You look where Ririn is pointing...
Haaaa!
Annihilate!
D-Damn you...!
>There is a male student fighting side by side with a demon.
Hmm, he's pretty good.
That's not the point! Normal boy! Demon!

Oh yeah, now that you mention it...
Hey kid! Yeah, you!
...Who are you people?
We're umm... I guess you can say we're here to take care of this situation.
This situation... So you know what's happening here?!
That's a no. We just started the investigation.
Oh, I see...
Do you know something about this place though?
This place...
I think it has something to do with my childhood friend's transformation.
